{"about_the_game":"Embark on a thrilling adventure in Aetheris, a tactical RPG with turn-based battles that combines roguelite and tabletop elements. Use your tactical skills, explore unforgettable environments and make the right choices to defeat the voracious Shade, and when the challenge gets to high call for backup in multiplayer coop!.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Skins_Steam_v2.png?t=1711714084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE GAME</strong></h2> <br>In Aetheris, every journey through the Wilderness is a unique adventure. Whether you brave the path alone or with companions, your decisions, the whims of fate, and the influence of mysterious entities will shape your destiny.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAIN FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A unique artistic direction</strong>: Journey through the seven regions of a hand-crafted and flamboyant Wilderness, each featuring their own atmosphere, soundtrack and storyline, for a truly immersive experience.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Vazzards_walking_gif_STEAM_VF.gif?t=1711714084\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Strategic Turn-Based Battles</strong>: Engage in tactical turn-based battles against wild creatures. Use your skills strategically, exploit enemy weaknesses, and unleash devastating power to emerge victorious. Fight, die and emerge stronger accompanied by the Spirits of those who have fallen.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Vazzards_fighting_STEAM.gif?t=1711714084\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Personality-based Skill System</strong>: Learn new skills and abilities based on the personality you choose for your Vazzard, allowing for varied and strategic gameplay approaches.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Vazzards_build_gif_STEAM_VF.gif?t=1711714084\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Choose your own path</strong>: Unpredictable events will spice up your journey, introducing unexpected encounters, opportunities, and dangers. Choose your path wisely, as your choices will profoundly impact the unfolding story.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Vazzard_choice.gif?t=1711714084\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Cooperative Multiplayer</strong>: Team-up as a party of four companions and face the dangers of the Wilderness for even greater challenges! Cooperate and survive together or tragically die trying.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Multi_coop_STEAM.gif?t=1711714084\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Race Against the Shade</strong>: Time is of the essence as the menacing Shade relentlessly pursues you. Stay one step ahead, adapt your strategies, and race against the encroaching darkness.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/Vazzards_running_from_the_Shade_STEAM_VF.gif?t=1711714084\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Botany","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1786010/ee754d5b1057db62f870f3744d87b67e07f0e5ba.jpg"},{"name":"Bravado","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1786010/aa9eef1fdff6a563a92132b10cbe60a26ca374b3.jpg"},{"name":"Snare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1786010/ce7ef12a8749655e67faedb546c408d36eee9b13.jpg"},{"name":"War cry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1786010/304a841b750f94ce558c6bf